OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWelsh government to        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapologise for forced       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fadoptions                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Welsh government is to formally    
OL,6, apologise to mothers forced to give    
OL,7, away their children.                   
OL,9,FThousands of unmarried women were      
OL,10,Fsubjected to forced adoptions in the   
OL,11,F1950s, '60s and '70s.                  
OL,13,FSpeaking in the Senedd, Deputy Social  
OL,14,FServices Minister Julie Morgan will say
OL,15,Fsorry for the failures in society that 
OL,16,Fled to the practice.                   
OL,18,FThe move was welcomed by campaigners   
OL,19,Fwho said the UK government should      
OL,20,Ffollow suit.                           
